This end-unit home offers a private feel, a car garage and a private, gated front courtyard. Enjoy a nice, wooded view as your new neighborhood is surrounded by ten beautiful, wooded acres and greenbelt, a walking trail and a sports court. Great location, this affordable condo is close to State offices, restaurants, parks and the highway for easy commuting. Schedule your tour today!
